  var time = new Date();
  var endTime = time.getTime();
  var storefrontSetupStart = getCookie("storefrontSetupStart");

    getTime(storefrontSetupStart);
  }
  
  
  //gets value of inviteCreationStartTime cookie
  function getCookie(cname) {
    var name = cname + "=";
    var decodedCookie = decodeURIComponent(document.cookie);
    var ca = decodedCookie.split(';');
    for(var i = 0; i <ca.length; i++) {
        var c = ca[i];
        while (c.charAt(0) == ' ') {
            c = c.substring(1);
        }
        if (c.indexOf(name) == 0) {
            return c.substring(name.length, c.length);

    }
    return "";

  // sets cookie with time elapsed
  function getTime(startTime) {
    var total = (endTime - startTime);
    if(typeof total == "number" && total>0){
      total = total/1000;
      if(total > 1800) total == 1800;
      var cookieName  = "storefrontSetupTimeElapsed"; 
      var cookieValue = total;
      var cookiePath  = "/";
               
      document.cookie = cookieName+"="+cookieValue+"; path="+cookiePath;  //Set cookie

    } 
  }
     
</script>
